38:56.159 --> 39:00.485
We will not bring charges, and
your warrant depends upon ours.

39:00.515 --> 39:06.170
Brenda, think about what you're doing.

39:09.038 --> 39:11.666
Please, Fritz.

39:14.294 --> 39:17.461
This is a mistake.

39:21.228 --> 39:23.276
You tell me the truth
about what happened,

39:23.316 --> 39:27.583
you can sit here and
your parents go free.

39:29.421 --> 39:32.009
