–Mom!

43:14.315 --> 43:16.393
Give me back my boy!

43:26.656 --> 43:29.173
Are you ok?

43:33.078 --> 43:35.924
I take it that means I'm driving.

43:36.024 --> 43:38.551
Yes. Thank you.

43:38.601 --> 43:40.168
And you were very, very helpful.

43:40.208 --> 43:42.276
